author: Anonymous Beaker
title: Pset unkown error: with-limit: out of time.
question:
Hello,
I am receiving this error with my problem set for question 1:
Additional tests: error: with-limit: out of time.
I am not sure what this means and can't figure it out. All the other marks for this question are correct.
student_answer: That likely means one of the additional tests through your function is causing an infinite loop - a cycle is not being properly terminated by your function.
